{"id":271,"date":"2026-06-07T17:56:54","date_gmt":"2026-06-07T16:56:54","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/?p=271"},"modified":"2026-06-09T12:31:26","modified_gmt":"2026-06-09T11:31:26","slug":"welcome-to-peter-farrar-portraits","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/welcome-to-peter-farrar-portraits\/","title":{"rendered":"Welcome to Peter Farrar Portraits"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>After some time away, I am delighted to welcome you to <strong>Peter Farrar Portraits<\/strong>, the new home for my photography, creative projects, and photographic journey.<\/p>\n<p>Many of you will have noticed that <strong>Kenneth Light Studios<\/strong> quietly disappeared some time ago. Rather than simply replacing it, I wanted to create something that better reflects who I am as a photographer today and where I want to take my work in the future.<\/p>\n<p>Peter Farrar Portraits brings together my passion for portrait photography, visual storytelling, and the art of creating images that capture personality, character, and emotion. It will also serve as a place to share photography articles, behind-the-scenes insights, photographic experiences, and practical tips for photographers of all levels.<\/p>\n<p>You may also have noticed changes across my social media platforms. Instagram, X, Threads, and Facebook now all carry the <strong>Peter Farrar Portraits<\/strong> name, creating a consistent identity wherever you choose to follow my work.<\/p>\n<p>While the website is now live, this is only the beginning. Over the coming weeks and months I will continue refining the site, expanding the photography galleries, publishing new blog posts, and sharing fresh content as the project develops.<\/p>\n<p>Whether you are here because you enjoy portrait photography, are interested in photography techniques, or simply want to follow the next stage of my creative journey, I am grateful to have you here.<\/p>\n<p>Thank you for your continued support and encouragement over the years. I look forward to sharing much more with you as Peter Farrar Portraits grows.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Welcome, and watch this space for future updates.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>After some time away, I am delighted to welcome you to Peter Farrar [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":284,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[4],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-271","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-peterfarrarupdates"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/271","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=271"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/271\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":361,"href":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/271\/revisions\/361"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/284"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=271"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=271"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/peterfarrarportraits.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=271"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.or